 is a wine that has adapted perfectly to our Enate vineyards and exhibits what its name indicates: a marked spicy character (würzig, in German)."},{"id":"en_GB","ocurrence":1,"type":"STRING","value":"Its aromatic range is broad and exuberant, full of honey and floral hints. Unctuous and velvety mouthfeel, highlighting elegant aromas of roses and spices that lead to a silky, enveloping finish."},{"id":"fr_FR","ocurrence":0,"type":"STRING","value":"Le Gewürztraminer, chef-d'œuvre de la viticulture d'Europe centrale est un vin qui, tout en étant parfaitement adapté à nos vignobles d'Enate, présente ce que son nom indique déjà : un caractère épicé marqué (würzig, en allemand)."},{"id":"fr_FR","ocurrence":1,"type":"STRING","value":"Son éventail aromatique est large et exubérant, plein de nuances mielleuses et florales. bouche, il est onctueux et velouté, avec d'élégants arômes de roses et d'épices, qui laissent place à un arrière-goût soyeux et enveloppant."}]}]},{"id":"GestionComprasStock","type":"GROUPING","children":[{"id":"Calificacion1","type":"STRING","value":"AA"},{"id":"Calificacion2","type":"STRING","value":"BJ"},{"id":"Calificacion4","type":"STRING","value":"VV"},{"id":"Calificacion5","type":"STRING","value":"1U"},{"id":"TipoDeGestion","type":"STRING","value":"14"}]},{"id":"DimensionesYPeso","type":"GROUPING","children":[{"id":"UOM!Dimensiones!Unidad","type":"LOOKUP_TABLE","featureGroupID":"204","id_Ext":"347186090","value":"cm"},{"id":"UOM!PesoBruto!Unidad","type":"LOOKUP_TABLE","featureGroupID":"206","id_Ext":"347187090","value":"g"},{"id":"UOM!VolumenContenidoNeto!VolumenContenidoNeto","type":"NUMBER","value":"0.0"},{"id":"UOM!VolumenContenidoNeto!Unidad","type":"LOOKUP_TABLE","featureGroupID":"213","id_Ext":"347188090","value":"ml"},{"id":"PUM","type":"GROUPING","children":[{"id":"CantidadProducto","type":"NUMBER","value":"0.0"},{"id":"UnidadesProducto","type":"STRING","value":"000"}]}]},{"id":"ColoresYTallas","type":"GROUPING","children":[{"id":"ColorFabri